        <briefdescription>
<para>Register the send scheduler LwM2M objects and initialise state. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This installs the Scheduler Control (10523) and Sampling Rules (10524) objects and prepares bookkeeping needed by the cache filter helpers.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para>0 on success, or a negative errno if object registration fails. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
