        <detaileddescription>
<para>Hook this up via <ref refid="group__lwm2m__api_1gac4e7da0353914601c3ec101415c2e110" kindref="member">lwm2m_set_cache_filter</ref> for each cached resource you want the scheduler to control.</para>
